### SEND ETH
POST {{ethNode}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc":"2.0",
  "method":"eth_sendTransaction",
  "params":[{
    "from": "{{sugarDaddy}}",
    "to": "{{alice}}",
    "value": "{{amount}}"
  }],
  "id":1
}

### GET BALANCE
POST {{ethNode}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc":"2.0",
  "method":"eth_getBalance",
  "params":["{{roger}}",  "latest"],
  "id":1
}

### GET BLOCK NUMBER
